Even that early , I heard things that made me shudder . 
Those who came later , went home resolved to give up their rights rather than undergo a second experience of rowdyism . 
But it was a jubilee for the servant girls . 
Burroak , which , the year before , had a Republican majority of three hundred , now went for the Democrats by more than five hundred . 
The same party carried the State , electing their Governor by near twenty thousand . 
The Republicans would now have gladly repealed the bill giving us equal rights , but they were in a minority , and the Democrats refused to co operate . 
Mrs. Whiston barely escaped being defeated her majority was reduced from seven hundred to forty three . 
Eleven Democratic Assemblywomen and four Senatoresses were chosen , however , so that she had the consolation of knowing that her sex had gained , although her party had lost . 
She was still in good spirits It will all right itself in time , she said . 
You will readily guess , after what I have related , that I was not only not re elected to the Legislature , but that I was not even a candidate . 
